replies.body:
Agreed, weapon swap would be brilliant. I reckon make him a juggernaut. He's got that warrior spirit, that;
"I'll keep fighting before I go down" feel.  I too feel he'll need a thing or two to keep up with upcoming champions and play styles.

I believe his ult should be a knockback. But if he's getting a complete rework there should be some sort of weapon swap mechanic. 

{{champion:80}}
